    <div class="container">
        <h2>Installing & Using Kalami âœ…</h2>
        <ul>
            <li class="step">
                <p class="step-title">1. Download & Install:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1iIBZwRG2Pjba5gkhmgf5VrzrOnVGkhDL">Download the build file</a></li>
                    <li>Go to <a href="chrome://extensions/">chrome://extensions/</a>, click <strong>Load unpacked</strong> and select the downloaded file.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li class="step">
                <p class="step-title">2. Activate & Upload:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Open a <a href="https://chat.openai.com/">ChatGPT window</a> and click the new Kalami button on the right.</li>
                    <li>Choose <strong>'Upload Context'</strong>. upload your file, name it, and enable.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li class="step">
                <p class="step-title">3. Query:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Type a context-related query and click <strong>"Ask Kalami"</strong> found in the bottom right.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
